  "description": "MUTATE at maximum — all 8 voices active but at extreme low level and maximum decay. The XVC cross-coupling routes every voice into every other: a bloom of bioluminescent percussion below any recognisable drum structure. The sound is 90% reverb tail. What surfaces is never what was struck.",
